    , source: [SourceTalesFromTheYawningPortal]
    , description:
      [ P
        [ I "Wondrous item, uncommon"
        ]
      , P
        [ T "This whistle is carved from transparent crystal, and it resembles a tiny dragon curled up like a snail. The name Night Caller is etched on the whistle in Dwarvish runes. If a character succeeds on a DC 20 Intelligence (Arcana or History) check, the character recalls lore that says the duergar made several such whistles for various groups in an age past."
