        [ T "Choose a magical bonus of +1 to +3. This sword gains that bonus to its attack and damage rolls. For each point of bonus you choose for the sword, you take a corresponding penalty (-1 to -3) to your death saving throws. You can change this magical bonus each day at dawn."
