      [ P
        [ I "Armor (Shield), very rare (requires attunement)"
        ]
      , P
        [ T "This shield is made from the scale of an ancient white dragon. It has a rune burned into its outward-facing side. A character who examines the rune and succeeds on a DC 20 Intelligence (History) check recognizes it as an uven (\"enemy\" in Giant) rune that confers great power."
