        [ T "While holding the shield, you benefit from the following properties."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Winter's Friend."
        , T " You are immune to cold damage."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Deadly Rebuke."
        , T " Immediately after a creature hits you with a melee attack, you can use your reaction to deal 3d6 necrotic damage to that creature."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Bane."
        , T " You can cast the "
        , I "Bane"
        , T " spell from the shield (save DC 17). The spell does not require concentration and lasts for 1 minute. Once you cast the spell from the shield you can't do so again until you finish a short or long rest."
        ]
      , P
