  , { title: "Azuredge"
    , url: "https://dnd5e.wikidot.com//wondrous-items:azuredge"
    , rarity: [RarityLegendary]
    , itemtype: TypeWeapon (Just "battleaxe")
    , attunement: Attune Nothing
    , source: [SourceWaterdeepDragonHeist]
    , description:
      [ P
        [ I "Weapon (battleaxe), legendary (requires attunement)"
        ]
      , P
        [ T "Forged by the archwizard Ahghairon, this intelligent battleaxe was crafted to defend Waterdeep. Its current wielder is a former member of Force Grey named Meloon Wardragon, but the weapon is searching for a new owner."
        ]
      , P
        [ I "Azuredge"
        , T " has a solid steel handle etched with tiny runes, wrapped in blue dragon hide with a star sapphire set into the pommel. The axe head is forged from silver, electrum, and steel alloys whose edges constantly shimmer with a deep blue luminescence."
        ]
      , P
        [ T "You gain a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon. The "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:shield" "Shield"
        , T " spell provides no defense against the axe, which passes through that spell's barrier of magical force."
        ]
      , P
        [ T "When you hit a fiend or an undead with the axe, cold blue flames erupt from its blade and deal an extra 2d6 radiant damage to the target."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Hurling."
        , T " The battleaxe has 3 charges. You can expend 1 charge and make a ranged attack with the axe, hurling it as if it had the thrown property with a normal range of 60 feet and a long range of 180 feet. Whether it hits or misses, the axe flies back to you at the end of the current turn, landing in your open hand or al your feet in your space (as you choose). The axe regains all expended charges daily at dawn."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Illumination."
        , T " While holding the axe, you can use an action to cause the axe to glow blue or to quench the glow. This glow sheds bright light in a 30-foot radius and dim light for an additional 30 feet."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Sentience."
        , I "Azuredge"
        , T " is a sentient lawful neutral weapon with an Intelligence of 12, a Wisdom of 15, and a Charisma of 15. It has hearing and darkvision out to a range of 120 feet."
        ]
      , P
        [ T "The weapon communicates telepathically with its wielder and can speak, read, and understand Common. It has a calm, delicate voice. The weapon can sense the presence of non-lawful creatures within 120 feet of it."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Personality."
        , I "Azuredge"
        , T " is sworn to protect Waterdeep, and it desires to be wielded by a law-abiding person willing to dedicate everything to the city's defense. The weapon is patient and takes its time finding its ideal wielder."
        ]
      , P
        [ T "If someone tries to use "
        , I "Azuredge"
        , T " against its will, the axe can become ten times heavier than normal, and can magically adhere to any Medium or larger object or surface it comes into contact with. Once it does so, the axe can't be wielded. Nothing short of a "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:wish" "Wish"
        , T " spell can separate the axe from the item or surface to which it is adhered without destroying one or the other, though the axe can choose to end the effect at any time."
        ]
      ]
    }
  , { title: "Belashyrra's Beholder Crown"
    , url: "https://dnd5e.wikidot.com//wondrous-items:belashyrras-beholder-crown"
    , rarity: [RarityLegendary]
    , itemtype: TypeItem Nothing
    , attunement: Attune Nothing
    , source: [SourceEberronRisingFromTheLastWar]
    , description:
      [ P
        [ I "Wondrous item, legendary (requires attunement)"
        ]
      , P
        [ T "This symbiotic crown is carved from dark purple and mauve stone, with ten points like stalks set with gemstones resembling the eyestalks of a beholder. To attune to this item, you must wear it on your head for the entire attunement period, during which the crown's hidden tendrils burrow into your scalp to bond with your skull."
        ]
      , P
        [ T "While wearing the crown, you can see normally in darkness, both magical and nonmagical, to a distance of 120 feet."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Spells."
        , T " The crown has 10 charges. While wearing it, you can use an action to expend some of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it (spell save DC 16): "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:charm-person" "Charm Person"
        , T " (1 charge), "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:disintegrate" "Disintegrate"
        , T " (6 charges), "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:fear" "Fear"
        , T " (3 charges), "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:finger-of-death" "Finger of Death"
        , T " (7 charges), "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:flesh-to-stone" "Flesh to Stone"
        , T " (6 charges), "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:hold-person" "Hold Person"
        , T " (2 charges), "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:ray-of-enfeeblement" "Ray of Enfeeblement"
        , T " (2 charges), "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:sleep" "Sleep"
        , T " (1 charge), "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:slow" "Slow"
        , T " (3 charges), "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:telekinesis" "Telekinesis"
        , T " (5 charges)."
        ]
      , P
        [ T "The crown regains 1d6 + 3 expended charges daily at dawn."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Symbiotic Nature."
        , T " The crown can't be removed from you while you're attuned to it, and you can't voluntarily end your attunement to it. If you're targeted by a spell that ends a curse, your attunement to the crown ends, and it detaches from you."
        ]
      , P
        [ T "The daelkyr Belashyrra made these crowns. While on the same plane of existence as the crown, Belashyrra can see through its eyestalks."
        ]
      ]
    }
  , { title: "Black Crystal Tablet"
    , url: "https://dnd5e.wikidot.com//wondrous-items:black-crystal-tablet"
    , rarity: [RarityLegendary]
