        [ B "Lingering Shock."
        , T " If you deal lightning damage to a creature, it can't take reactions until its next turn."
        ]
      , H3 "Green Dragon Mask"
      , P
        [ T "This mottled green mask is surmounted by a frilled crest and has leathery spiked plates along its jaw. Its damage type is poison. While you wear the mask, you gain the following benefit, in addition to those the dragon masks share."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Water Breathing."
        , T " You can breathe underwater."
        ]
      , H3 "Red Dragon Mask"
