        , T " for 24 consecutive hours, barnacles form on your skin. The barnacles can be removed with a "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:greater-restoration" "Greater Restoration"
        , T " spell or similar magic, but not while you are attuned to the weapon."
        ]
      ]
    }
  , { title: "Efreeti Chain"
