        , T ", "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:locate-creature" "Locate Creature"
        , T ", "
        , A "http://dnd5e.wikidot.com/spell:transport-via-plants" "Transport Via Plants"
        , T ". Once you use the shield to cast a spell, the shield can't cast that spell again until the next dawn."
        ]
      ]
    }
  , { title: "Fane-Eater"
