      , P
        [ B "Sentience."
        , T " Nepenthe is a sentient neutral evil weapon with an Intelligence of 10, a Wisdom of 8, and a Charisma of 18. It has hearing and darkvision out to a range of 60 feet. It can read and understand Elvish. It can also speak Elvish, but only through the voice of its wielder, with whom the sword can communicate telepathically."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Personality."
        , T " In its lifetime, the sword has beheaded thousands of criminals, not all of whom were guilty of the crimes for which they were convicted. The sword cannot distinguish the guilty from the innocent. With each beheading, it hungers for more justice and blood. The sword is corrupt and irredeemable."
        ]
      ]
    }
  , { title: "Nether Scroll of Azumar"
    , url: "https://dnd5e.wikidot.com//wondrous-items:nether-scroll-of-azumar"
    , rarity: [RarityLegendary]
    , itemtype: TypeScroll
    , attunement: AttuneNone
    , source: [SourceCandlekeepMysteries]
    , description:
      [ P
        [ I "Scroll, legendary"
        ]
      , P
        [ T "Unlike most scrolls, a Nether Scroll of Azumar is not a consumable magic item. It takes 30 days of concentrated study-at least 8 hours per day-to attempt to understand this scroll. After completing this study, you must make a DC 25 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If this check fails, you take 16d10 psychic damage, and you can attempt the check again after another 30 days of concentrated study."
        ]
      , P
        [ T "When you succeed on the check, you gain the following benefits:"
        ]
      , UL
        [ 
          [ T "Your Intelligence score increases by 2, to a maximum of 22. Once you gain this benefit, you can't use this scroll to increase your Intelligence again."
          ]
        , 
          [ T "You gain advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects."
          ]
        ]
      , P
        [ T "When you gain the scroll's benefits, a stone golem magically appears in an unoccupied space within 60 feet of you and acts as your ally. If you die, the golem turns to dust."
        ]
      ]
    }
  , { title: "Nightbringer"
    , url: "https://dnd5e.wikidot.com//wondrous-items:nightbringer"
    , rarity: [RarityLegendary]
    , itemtype: TypeWeapon (Just "mace")
    , attunement: Attune Nothing
    , source: [SourceMonstrousCompendium2]
    , description:
      [ P
        [ I "Weapon (Mace), Legendary (Requires Attunement)"
