      , P
        [ T "You gain a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this weapon. When you hit with an attack roll using it, the target takes an additional 4d4 radiant damage."
        ]
      , P
        [ T "If you have an evil alignment, you also gain the following benefits when attuned to Nightbringer:"
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Blessing of the Dragon Queen."
