    , source: [SourcePrincesOfTheApocalypse]
    , description:
      [ P
        [ I "Weapon (dagger), legendary (requires attunement)"
        ]
      , P
        [ T "A flint dagger, "
        , I "Tinderstrike"
        , T " is uncommonly sharp, and sparks cascade off its edge whenever it strikes something solid. Its handle is always warm to the touch, and the blade smolders for 1d4 minutes after it is used to deal damage. It contains a spark of Imix, Prince of Evil Fire."
        ]
      , P
        [ T "You gain a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls you make with this magic weapon. When you hit with it, the target takes an extra 2d6 fire damage."
        ]
