      , P
        [ B "Thrown Weapon."
        , I "Whelm"
        , T " has the thrown property, with a normal range of 20 feet and a long range of 60 feet. When you hit with a ranged weapon attack using it, the target takes an extra 1d8 bludgeoning damage, or an extra 2d8 bludgeoning damage if the target is a giant. Each time you throw the weapon, it flies back to your hand after the attack. If you don't have a hand free, the weapon lands at your feet."
        ]
      , P
        [ B "Shock Wave."
        , T " You can use an action to strike the ground with "
